Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:18.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:22.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:26.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:33.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:51.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:54.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:59.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:03.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:11.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:15.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,190.389)}Steel Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs195\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,680.389)}Armadillong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think a plane crashed, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's check it out!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a big hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it came from outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It could have!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving! That thing's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Screwball Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, get inside! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot escape me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Screwball Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that, men?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the power of Armadillong,\Njust sent from Brazil to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel, what's his objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Blowing up gasholders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Armadillong will blow up\Ngasholders across Tokyo and Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The flames that rise from the wreckage\Nwill burn Tokyo and Osaka to cinders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That task is much too easy\Nfor one of Armadillong's talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have him first defeat our mortal\Nenemy, the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol, the man from\Nthe mountain cottage...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Armadillong, dispose of him at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing at this early hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of new case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mysterious explosion near\NMount Wakagoma Cottage?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"At 4 PM yesterday,\Na mountain cottage blew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The local villagers were crushed inside..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what Hayato's after?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two! One, two! One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you dressed up like that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just what it looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Early morning training!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't interrupt your sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're the sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a nice way to start your day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,After practice is over, you all\Nget Kamen Rider pendants?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Susumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You, call an ambulance! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... that man did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. That man is my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri's playing karate teacher again,\Nusing pendants to lure in the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, teaching karate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This I have to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me! Give me that pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get a grip!\N- Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two! One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- One!\N- One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two!\N- Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- One!\N- One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two!\N- Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- One!\N- One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two!\N- Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- One!\N- One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two!\N- Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Susumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't skip out, Susumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or you won't get your pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Susumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they went home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Susumu's shoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The kids were pretty keen\Nto get these pendants...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What would they be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Could something have happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... this way, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a faithful daughter, Connie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You pursued me all the way to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But a foolish human like you\Nis no match for Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not strong enough\Nto beat him. Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me, Shocker monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... it's like his body's made of steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've caught on at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Screwball Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato... adios!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shocker is here...\NArmadillong must be nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who are you?\N- I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you take Yuri and the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed my mother,\Nmy father, and my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... feel the\Npower of my Screwball Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:32.87,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Connie Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Armadillong killed my family\Nsix months ago, in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We had such a happy life together...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then suddenly, one night,\Nthat monster appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a Shocker\Ncyborg target your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker was testing Armadillong...\NThat was the only reason it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By some miracle, I made it out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you came all the way\Nfrom Brazil after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I will defeat Armadillong\Nno matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Armadillong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name will be honored\Nforever in the annals of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Kamen Rider gone,\NJapan is as good as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Japan Branch will now\Nbegin its all-out attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel, what should we do with\Nthe woman and children we took hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them a grand execution\Nin accordance with Shocker law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And invite Tachibana Tobei to come see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Invite him? A fine idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Show him the end that awaits\Nall who stand against Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see another pendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This way. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's watch and see what they're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see them... five of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to beat those five.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have two hostages in the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Any trouble we start could be bad for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a better way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Light this, and fire it\Ninto one of those trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,While Shocker is distracted,\NI'll charge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself! Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker HQ! Shocker HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Point A! Point A, respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Point A here. Nothing to report!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The base is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they abandon their base?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A mannequin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew you'd infiltrated our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's delay gratification\Nand execute you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A missing persons report?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you wait a moment longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Yuri is with him, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world did she take Susumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she know his parents are worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please join us at the base of Mount Kitamine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to watch the grand execution\Nof your club members."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The base of Mount Kitamine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look alive, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep walking, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to push you off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Shocker execution ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the kid go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get him!\N- Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,His stomach is his weak point...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Screwball Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider beat the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We beat Armadillong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, your home, Japan...\NIt's a truly wonderful country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But we know Shocker... they\Ncould be plotting anything next!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister, where'd Rider go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:27.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato, the Kamen Rider,\Nshattered Armadillong's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:33.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But let us not forget behind it all,\Nirreplaceable lives are being lost
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.38,0:23:35.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that we may never hear about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:40.58,Cont,,0,50,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.48,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:46.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the toad monster, Gamagiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:50.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's latest horrifying\Nplan is to split Japan in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:54.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our Kamen Rider learns of the plot,\Nand pursues Gamagiller to a secret airfield!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:56.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:24:01.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Japan in Peril! Gamagiller's Invasion"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:24:01.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(457.167,210.389)}Japan in Peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:24:01.10,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,660.389)}Gamagiller's Invasion"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:10.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:13.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:15.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.30,0:24:18.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:20.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:22.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:24.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.39,0:24:25.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:28.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:33.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.95,0:24:37.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.53,0:24:41.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.62,0:24:45.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Steel Monster Armadillong